com.microsoft.azure.storage.core

Class Logger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.storage.core.Logger

  • public class Logger
extends java.lang.Object
    RESERVED FOR INTERNAL USE. A wrapper around an andruild.util.Log object which allows for performance optimizations around string formatting, better formatted log descriptions, and more library control over when to log.
